    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely gotta see this beauty. It's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014completely flawless inside and out! I've babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh, new-car feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s in truly pristine shape and ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, I promise you're going to love it! \u2728",
