      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Available now is a breathtaking example of automotive excellence, maintained in what can only be described as showroom condition. This vehicle has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep factory luster with zero stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are free of any curb rash, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state; the leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear or bolster compression, and the high-gloss trim pieces are devoid of scratches. All interior electronics, including the infotainment and climate control systems, operate exactly as they did the day the car left the factory. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a complete, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, reflecting the meticulous care this vehicle has received. This sale includes all original keys, the full suite of owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title. For the buyer seeking a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle, this is an unmatched opportunity.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
