    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one\u2014always garaged, no pets, and definitely no smoking. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
