    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative specimen of the S54-powered era. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features perfectly synchronized double VANOS and razor-sharp individual throttle body response. This example is mechanically pristine, featuring documented rod bearing replacement and proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Power is transmitted via a crisp six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster with zero panel misalignment, while the interior's Nappa leather bolsters show no sign of compression or wear. A collector-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who values mechanical transparency and performance purity.",
